Package: AdvDeltaChange
Type: Package
Title: Perform Advanced Delta Change on Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Vera", "Vavan", "veravavan@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Vera Vavan <veravavan@gmail.com>
Description: This package can extract data from rasters, derive the delta change parameters, transform observed series
    into climate change scenarios and visualize the results. It uses .txt files for observed data and .nc files for
    simulated data.
License: `use_mit_license()`
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
Imports: 
    ncdf4,
    data.table,
    raster,
    terra
URL: https://github.com/veravavan/AdvDeltaChange
BugReports: https://github.com/veravavan/AdvDeltaChange/issues
